{"tid":1136403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"MegaBox健身男由跑步機跌下　疑隱性病發猝死","createTime":"2019-05-03T03:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T03:41:44.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"653376f522c692bbe6b18d09705fb83cff2537e0","tid":1136403,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:41:44.000Z","msg":"昨日（2日）晚上10時許，九龍灣宏照道MegaBox商場一間連鎖健身中心內，一名45歲姓曾男子在跑步機上運動時，被職員發現跌倒地上，立即上前施援，惟他已陷昏迷。職員於是報警求助，事主由救護車送往聯合醫院急救後，證實不治。警方經初步調查，相信無可疑，懷疑事主隱性病發作猝死，需剖驗才能確定致死原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190503/bkn-20190503003123468-0503_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190503%2Fbkn-20190503003123468-0503_00822_001.html&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=4e974495\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190503/bkn-20190503003123468-0503_00822_001.html</a>"}]}